title: Ep 22 - Stop Saying "I Wish" & Start Saying "I Will"
itunes:title: Ep 22 - Stop Saying "I Wish" & Start Saying "I Will"
description:
It is time to take control of your life and stop making excuses. Whatever it is you want in this life you can have, you just need to have the mental fortitude to work hard for it and not allow yourself to make excuses. In this episode we speak about how the gym is a perfect metaphor for life and how you do one thing is how you do everything.
